   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Apollodoros and Herakleides. Keneus, sitologos, reports that 10 1/2 artabas of wheat have been measured out by N.N. son of Pyla[-], kleros-holder in Neseus for the 31st year, that is, 10 1/2 art. The 31st year, Mesore 18th.</ab>
